        <heading>Section </heading>
        <content>
          <p>SECTION 3.  JUDGMENT OF POSSESSION
Art. 3381.  Judgment of possession
A judgment of possession shall be rendered and signed as provided in Article 3061.  The judgment shall be rendered and signed only after a hearing contradictory with the succession representative, unless he joins in the petition, in which event the judgment shall be rendered and signed immediately.</p>
        </content>
